data.text:
Adelaide of Austria and Victor Emmanuel II of Italy were married for 12 years before Adelaide of Austria died, leaving behind her partner and 8 children.

They had 8 children, Maria Clotilde (181), Umberto (180), Amadeo (179), Oddone (177), Maria Pia (177), Carlo Alberto (173), Vittorio Emanuele (171) and Vittorio Emanuele (169).
